T02TD2411E:32b-1: tsa tur buddha bha ba bhya ba sha nam kra mam n'a ma /
T02TD2411E:32b-3: 'byung ba bzhi'i srid pa'i chags lugs zhes bya ba //
T02TD2411E:32b-4: thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2411E:32b-5: ri rab zur ni brgyad pa dang //
T02TD2411E:32b-6: rol pa'i mtsho ni bdun pa dang //
T02TD2411E:32b-7: tshangs pa brgya byin nyi ma dang //
T02TD2411E:32b-8: zla ba dang ni lha chen dang //
T02TD2411E:32b-9: mthu chen 'di dag rtag min na //
T02TD2411E:32b-10: bdag gis ji ltar brtan pa thob //
T02TD2411E:32b-11: bdag ni brtag na ji ltar yin //
T02TD2411E:32b-12: bdag gi ma ni gang du song //
T02TD2411E:32b-13: pha yang gang du song bar 'gyur //
T02TD2411E:32b-16: stobs ldan gyur na sus kyang bkur //
T02TD2411E:32b-17: stobs nyams gyur na smra mi byed //
T02TD2411E:32b-18: de bas tshem bu'i gos gyon la //
T02TD2411E:32b-19: bsod snyoms kyis ni 'tsho ba ste //
T02TD2411E:32b-20: yul dang grong khyer so ma ru //
T02TD2411E:32b-21: yang yang sprang ba mkhas pa yin //
T02TD2411E:32b-22: 'di lta bu yi spyod pa yis //
T02TD2411E:32b-23: 'jig rten kun la rgyal ba thob //
T02TD2411E:32b-24: skal ldan bdag ni tsa ra pa tri smra //
T02TD2411E:32b-25: 'byung ba bzhi'i srid pa'i chags lugs zhes bya ba slob dpon tsa ra pa tri sa mdzad pa rdzogs so /
